    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【第一章数千玩家96%好评率的视觉小说迎来全新第二章！】</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当阿凡达的异星奇观碰上怪奇的悬疑氛围，再加入克苏鲁的古神恐惧——本作就是为你量身定制的奇幻恐怖故事！动态背景与漫画式分镜的视觉冲击将让你在游戏的世界中身临其境，每一次对话选择都将带来不同的结果，改写角色甚至世界的命运。在你迷茫的时候，平行世界的“伙伴”或许会为你的决定带来关键启示！现在就进入这个世界，来书写属于你的奇幻故事吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2075630/extras/bc1e3edf5430be7f815eb6cdda69759c.poster.avif?t=1764820776\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2075630/extras/bc1e3edf5430be7f815eb6cdda69759c.webm?t=1764820776\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2075630/extras/bc1e3edf5430be7f815eb6cdda69759c.mp4?t=1764820776\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2075630/extras/9d7db4c31b2042bc8fcecddfd252c9f5.avif?t=1764820776\" width=616 height=106 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这个世界里，生存着一种可以与环境互动的种族——扎阿尼族。他们虔诚地守护着家园以换取食物和庇护。但命运从不公平：只有少数幸运儿能觉醒德鲁伊之力，探索未知的领域；而大多数扎阿尼人，终其一生都只能被困在这里。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >艾妮莉亚，一个怀揣着成为德鲁伊梦想的普通扎阿尼少女，即将踏上一场改变命运的旅程。但等待她的不仅是未知的奇遇，还有来自远古的致命古神诅咒——疯狂。是成为救赎的希望，还是堕入毁灭的深渊？一切由你来决定！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2075630/extras/ab9f992862142c611bbd66692f6177fb.poster.avif?t=1764820776\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2075630/extras/ab9f992862142c611bbd66692f6177fb.webm?t=1764820776\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2075630/extras/ab9f992862142c611bbd66692f6177fb.mp4?t=1764820776\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2075630/extras/14b983b41d48730be4650dbe0dc7d772.avif?t=1764820776\" width=616 height=106 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这段充满未知的旅程中，你将遇见形形色色的扎阿尼人——他们可能是生死与共的伙伴，与你并肩对抗远古的恐惧；也可能是暗藏杀机的背叛者，在关键时刻给你致命一击...或者，他们同时具备这两种身份。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2075630/extras/9b0fe57cde4575ea6ff0442a9335d310.poster.avif?t=1764820776\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2075630/extras/9b0fe57cde4575ea6ff0442a9335d310.webm?t=1764820776\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2075630/extras/9b0fe57cde4575ea6ff0442a9335d310.mp4?t=1764820776\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: right\">当信任与怀疑交织时，你的心会指引你走向何方？每个选择都在重塑你与他们的羁绊，而这份羁绊将决定他们的生死存亡。当疯狂席卷而来，爱与背叛只有一线之隔...记住，在这个世界里，没有绝对的对错——只有属于你的独特故事！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2075630/extras/616c8136a10ea1da10fae7254e6fa3d8.poster.avif?t=1764820776\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2075630/extras/616c8136a10ea1da10fae7254e6fa3d8.webm?t=1764820776\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2075630/extras/616c8136a10ea1da10fae7254e6fa3d8.mp4?t=1764820776\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2075630/extras/43bf668cf1878448c73b23e540aa9f0b.avif?t=1764820776\" width=616 height=106 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这场震撼心灵的旅程中，你将穿梭于不同角色的视角，亲历平行时空中正在上演的冒险故事。每个身份都为你揭开故事的全新维度——当你能同时看见命运的两面，你的选择会改变吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >五种以上的结局等待你的解锁，从疯狂信徒到救世英雄，每条道路都镌刻着你独特的意志。和艾妮莉亚一起来迎接这场直击心灵的冒险吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2075630/extras/73498fd9778c16b2f309fe505a2aea30.poster.avif?t=1764820776\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2075630/extras/73498fd9778c16b2f309fe505a2aea30.webm?t=1764820776\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2075630/extras/73498fd9778c16b2f309fe505a2aea30.mp4?t=1764820776\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
